CHANGELOG
#########

1.0.3 (2009-07-29)
Major bug fixes and improved conditional checks to ensure things are a bit more
sane. Fewer build errors should slip through now resulting in partly broken 
installs. Also improved the MySQL LaunchDaemon configuration file.

1.0.2 (2009-07-29)
Updated git build to version 1.6.4.1.

1.0.1 (2009-07/29)
Changed download link for Pound. Primary download URL is currently unavailable.

1.0 (2009-07-27)
Initial rewritten release includes 64bit-ready source installs for Snow Leopard.